My father, then, he gathered money, he gathered 
money. That was what my grandfather, my father,

09:06.374 --> 09:08.657
did. They gathered money, so I think they met with 
the first boss that I knew, that I thought, that I

09:09.228 --> 09:23.011
thought that my father had that boss. It was Mr. 
Yondón. Yondón. Yondón. Yondón. Uh-huh. His name

09:30.344 --> 09:32.367
was Juan Yondón. Yes. Yes. By the way, they live 
around the 9th before they reach Corpus. They

09:38.820 --> 09:46.132
don't exist anymore, but I think one or two of his 
daughters do exist. Yes. His place is still there,

09:47.595 --> 09:52.823
because it was a very beautiful place. I remember 
he was a fat man. very pink, with a white beard, and

09:57.254 --> 10:06.949
he wore a big hat, and he was a very respectful man. 
