10:22.685 --> 10:23.606
What part? Well, I didn't know what part he was from 
because when I thought about it, it was that he

10:24.067 --> 10:35.681
lived there, he had all his property. I think, who 
knows, he was the first founder of here because he

10:35.701 --> 10:44.831
had a very beautiful house. It was worth a lot of 
money because the house still exists. Well,

10:51.355 --> 10:59.671
my father worked with him for many years. Then my 
father worked with a man, his name was Jose Han. He

