don't know if that man was the fourth, or the 
middle, or I don't know how he did with his boss. But

23:20.919 --> 23:27.045
then, my father always bought the best. With what 
God gave him, he bought skulls, all kinds of tools

23:35.017 --> 23:38.303
that he needed to work, he would buy them. He 
thought about all that because he looked and

23:38.324 --> 23:46.319
because his boss told him.

23:49.105 --> 23:52.191
